00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,447
Jamal Malik je samo jedno pitanje
od osvajanja 20 milijuna rupija.

5
00:01:34,482 --> 00:01:36,119
kako je to uspio?

6
00:01:36,154 --> 00:01:38,008
A: Varao je

7
00:01:38,043 --> 00:01:39,616
B: Imao je sree

8
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,668
C: On je genij

9
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,178
D: Napisano je

10
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,965
Dobra veer!

11
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:58,275
Dobrodoli u "Milijunaa"!

12
00:02:00,035 --> 00:02:02,000
jeste li spremni?

13
00:02:02,035 --> 00:02:04,765
Da.

14
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:10,000
Molim veliki pljesak za prvog
natjecatelja danas,

15
00:02:10,035 --> 00:02:14,557
Jamal Malik iz naeg Mumbaya!

16
00:02:17,035 --> 00:02:18,213
Idemo se igrati.

17
00:02:27,071 --> 00:02:28,730
Osmijeh, bit e sve u redu.

18
00:02:30,035 --> 00:02:32,965
Ime.

19
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:38,388
Ime!

20
00:02:38,389 --> 00:02:40,165
Jamal Malik.

21
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:44,393
Ima ime. Odlino. Prestani
plakati.

22
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Hvala. Hvala. Hvala puno.

23
00:02:53,035 --> 00:02:53,965
Onda, Jamal...

24
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:58,608
reci mi neto o sebi.

25
00:03:00,035 --> 00:03:03,000
Radim u pozivnom centru

26
00:03:03,035 --> 00:03:05,517
u Juhu. -Dobro.

27
00:03:05,552 --> 00:03:07,965
Operator na telefonu...

28
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,000
A kakav je to pozivni centar?

29
00:03:11,035 --> 00:03:12,824
XL5 mobiteli.

30
00:03:12,825 --> 00:03:14,732
Znai ti si taj koji me
zove

31
00:03:14,905 --> 00:03:17,211
svaku veer sa posebnim
ponudama, ha?

32
00:03:19,035 --> 00:03:21,000
Ne, zapravo, ja sam samo
pomonik.

33
00:03:21,035 --> 00:03:25,965
Pomoni operater na pozivima?

34
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:30,000
A to pomoni operater
tono radi?

35
00:03:30,035 --> 00:03:34,517
Donosim aj ljudima i...

36
00:03:34,552 --> 00:03:38,276
Posluitelj. Posluitelj.

37
00:03:38,311 --> 00:03:41,965
Pa, dame i gospodo,

38
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,126
Jamal Malik... posluitelj
iz Mumbaya,

39
00:03:45,127 --> 00:03:48,123
Idemo igrati "Milijunaa"!

40
00:03:58,035 --> 00:03:59,965
Onda, je li ve priznao?

41
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,965
Osim imena nisam uspio
nita izvui iz njega.

42
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:07,000
Ovdje si cijelu prokletu no,
Srinivas. to si do sad radio?

43
00:04:07,035 --> 00:04:08,965
Teak je.

44
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:12,000
Malo struje e mu opustiti
jezik. Daj mu.

45
00:04:12,035 --> 00:04:13,206
Da, gospodine.

46
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:25,000
Kako si bio spojen?

47
00:04:25,035 --> 00:04:27,965
Mobitel ili pager?

48
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Ili neki suuesnik u publici
koji se zakaljavao?

49
00:04:32,035 --> 00:04:36,274
Ili mikrofon ispod koe, ha?

50
00:04:41,035 --> 00:04:43,565
ip nije ovdje.

51
00:04:43,566 --> 00:04:46,591
Nije tu? Ok, ostavi.

52
00:04:47,692 --> 00:04:50,696
Vrue je, i moja ena me
zafrkava.

53
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,340
Imam stol pun ubojstava,
silovatelja,

54
00:04:54,635 --> 00:04:59,609
iznuivaa, bombaa, i ti.

55
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:06,628
Zato nam onda obojici ne bi
utedio vrijeme

56
00:05:06,777 --> 00:05:10,116
i rekao mi kako si varao.

57
00:05:25,035 --> 00:05:31,017
Gotov sam, gospodine.

58
00:05:31,052 --> 00:05:34,217
Sluaj me sad.

59
00:05:36,394 --> 00:05:38,748
Halo!

60
00:05:41,149 --> 00:05:43,048
U nesvijesti je, chutiya.
Kako mi to moe pomoi?

61
00:05:43,349 --> 00:05:45,726
Koliko puta ti trebam rei da
bi trebao...

62
00:05:46,852 --> 00:05:48,051
Oprostite, gospodine.

63
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,000
Sad e nam ovdje doi
Amnesty International

64
00:05:51,035 --> 00:05:54,000
i plakati nam o ljudskim pravima.

65
00:05:54,035 --> 00:05:54,965
Gospodine, mislio sam...

66
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:59,000
Skini ga dole i sredi ga.
Za ime Boga!

67
00:05:59,035 --> 00:06:04,965
Gospodine, to ako je
stvarno znao odgovore?

68
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:08,000
Profesori, doktori, advokati,
ljudi koji puno znaju

69
00:06:08,035 --> 00:06:10,000
nisu nikad doli dalje od
60.000 rupija.

70
00:06:10,035 --> 00:06:11,965
On je na 10 milijuna.

71
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:18,000
to taj bijednik iz
geta moe znati?

72
00:06:18,035 --> 00:06:25,035
Odgovore.

73
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:31,500
Znam odgovore.

74
00:06:31,535 --> 00:06:36,767
MILIJUNA IZ GETA

75
00:06:36,802 --> 00:06:40,451
Jamal, uhvati!

76
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:44,591
Jamal, tvoja je!

77
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:54,146
Kako si uspio ispustiti tako
dobru loptu?

78
00:06:54,181 --> 00:06:56,757
Privatni aerodrom!

79
00:06:59,035 --> 00:07:00,769
Uhvati ga!

80
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,527
Psi dolaze! Bjei!

81
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,559
Ako vas avioni ne ubiju, mi emo!

82
00:07:15,035 --> 00:07:17,224
Hej brate!

83
00:08:46,035 --> 00:08:48,330
ao mi je!

84
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,577
Jako mi je ao.

85
00:09:03,345 --> 00:09:05,059
Oh sranje, to je mama.

86
00:09:05,094 --> 00:09:06,504
Hoe li da te prebijem na
mrtvo ime, ha?

87
00:09:08,035 --> 00:09:10,948
Brate, ostavi ova dva meni.

88
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,488
Idemo.

89
00:09:17,368 --> 00:09:19,001
Athos.

90
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:26,236
Tri muketira.

91
00:09:26,237 --> 00:09:30,040
Ponovi! "Zvali ste me, gospodine?"
rekao je Athos.

92
00:09:32,361 --> 00:09:35,509
Ah, dolaze nai pravi muketiri.

93
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,115
Hvala Vam to ste nas poastili
svojom prisutnou.

94
00:09:40,035 --> 00:09:41,170
Porthos!

95
00:09:41,205 --> 00:09:42,835
Pa, otvori, Salim.

96
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,331
Prestani to raditi i otvori
knjigu, Jamal.

97
00:09:49,435 --> 00:09:50,249
Athos?

98
00:10:09,479 --> 00:10:12,226
Onda... g. Malik

99
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:15,548
ovjek koji zna sve odgovore.

100
00:10:18,036 --> 00:10:18,966
Priaj.

101
00:10:20,637 --> 00:10:22,150
Govori!

102
00:10:27,274 --> 00:10:31,231
Onda, Jamal, jesi li spreman za
prvo pitanje, za 1000 rupija?

103
00:10:32,035 --> 00:10:33,965
Da.

104
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,000
Nije loe za samo sjediti
na stolici

105
00:10:35,035 --> 00:10:36,965
i odgovarati na pitanje.

106
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:40,000
Bolje nego praviti aj, zar ne?

107
00:10:40,035 --> 00:10:41,965
Ne. Da. Ne.

108
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:46,500
Ne? Da? Ne? Je li to tvoj
konani odgovor?

109
00:10:46,535 --> 00:10:51,000
Zapamti. Ima tri pomoi.

110
00:10:51,035 --> 00:10:55,000
Pitaj publiku, pola-pola

111
00:10:55,035 --> 00:10:56,965
i pozovi prijatelja.

112
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:00,859
Prvo pitanje, za 1000 rupija,
idemo.

113
00:11:01,035 --> 00:11:07,857
Tko je bio glavna zvijezda u filmu
iz 1973., "Zanjeer"?

114
00:11:18,035 --> 00:11:19,692
Gusto mi je ovdje...

115
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:25,999
Evo... Novac. Uzmi novac...

116
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:33,000
Izlazi, Jamal.
Prakash mora na veliku nudu.

117
00:11:34,035 --> 00:11:36,999
Nisam gotov.

118
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,132
Pregrizi. Ovo je hitno...

119
00:11:39,133 --> 00:11:41,326
Ide polako van...

120
00:11:41,327 --> 00:11:44,119
i od kada postoji vremensko
ogranienje za sranje?

121
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:46,965
Pri kraju sam, mali. Pouri...

122
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:51,000
Muterija eka,
pouri Jamal!

123
00:11:51,035 --> 00:11:54,000
Vrati mi novac!
Daj! Idem na drugo mjesto.

124
00:11:54,035 --> 00:11:56,965
Glupi idiot.

125
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:01,000
Kotao si me muterije.

126
00:12:01,035 --> 00:12:03,965
Amitabhov helikopter!

127
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,235
To je Amitabhov helikopter!

128
00:12:05,833 --> 00:12:06,705
Amitabh!

129
00:12:08,922 --> 00:12:11,420
Amitabh Bachchan!

130
00:12:27,236 --> 00:12:28,280
Salim, otvori!

131
00:13:09,509 --> 00:13:11,654
Amitabh Bachchan!

132
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,877
Amitabh, gospodine!

133
00:13:30,629 --> 00:13:32,237
Makni se! makni se s puta!

134
00:13:32,272 --> 00:13:34,783
Molim te ekaj, dolazim!

135
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:39,846
Amitabh, gospodine,
dajte mi molim Vas autogram.

136
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:07,940
Ima ga sad, zar ne?
Amitabhov autogram?

137
00:14:44,073 --> 00:14:46,661
To je bio moj autogram!

138
00:14:46,696 --> 00:14:48,710
Amitabh mi ga je dao!

139
00:14:48,811 --> 00:14:50,519
Nikad neu dobiti jo jedan!

140
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:54,034
Ponudio je dobru cijenu, pas
sam ga prodao.

141
00:14:54,102 --> 00:14:56,330
Ali bio je moj...

142
00:14:57,552 --> 00:15:00,965
A, Amitabh Bachchan.

143
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,986
Zna to, u pravu si. Upravo
si osvojio 1,000 rupija.

144
00:15:08,035 --> 00:15:09,481
Ne treba biti genije.

145
00:15:09,593 --> 00:15:12,075
Znao sam da je to Amitabh Bachchan.

146
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,503
Kao to sam rekao, ne treba
biti genije.

147
00:15:20,035 --> 00:15:21,906
On je najpoznatiji ovjek u
Indiji.

148
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:28,067
Slika tri lava koja stoji na
nacionalnom grbu Indije.

149
00:15:29,035 --> 00:15:31,438
to pie ispod?

150
00:15:32,052 --> 00:15:35,043
A: Samo istina pobjeuje

151
00:15:35,078 --> 00:15:38,262
B: Samo la pobjeuje

152
00:15:38,552 --> 00:15:41,122
C: Samo moda pobjeuje

153
00:15:41,928 --> 00:15:45,531
D: Samo novac pobjeuje

154
00:15:50,664 --> 00:15:52,465
to ti misli, Jamal?

155
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:56,910
Najpoznatija fraza u naoj zemlji.

156
00:15:57,035 --> 00:15:59,450
eli li pozvati prijatelja?

157
00:15:59,485 --> 00:16:01,965
Pitao bih publiku.

158
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,965
Tko e mu skratiti muke,
dame i gospodo?

159
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:08,000
Moja petogodinja ker zna
odgovor na to pitanje,

160
00:16:08,035 --> 00:16:09,387
ali ti nisi znao.

161
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:12,221
To je jako udno za milijunaa
genija.

162
00:16:13,035 --> 00:16:14,486
to se dogodilo?

163
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:18,000
Tvoj suuesnik je izaao van
na pianje?

164
00:16:18,035 --> 00:16:20,965
Inspektor te je neto pitao.

165
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:24,132
Koliko kota panipuri u
Dharisha duanu na Chowpattyu?

166
00:16:24,930 --> 00:16:26,339
to?

167
00:16:26,374 --> 00:16:29,830
Panipuri. Jedna plata. Koliko?

168
00:16:30,035 --> 00:16:32,034
10 rupija. -Krivo.

169
00:16:32,035 --> 00:16:33,021
15, od Diwalia.

170
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,634
Tko je Varmyu ukrao bicikl

171
00:16:37,635 --> 00:16:40,347
blizu Santa Cruz stanice
proli etvrtak?

172
00:16:42,035 --> 00:16:43,406
Zna tko je to bio?

173
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,000
Svatko u Juhuu zna to.

174
00:16:46,035 --> 00:16:48,855
ak i petogodinjaci.

175
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:55,953
estitam, Jamal.
Osvojio si 4,000 rupija.

176
00:17:01,035 --> 00:17:03,285
16 tisua rupija.

177
00:17:05,552 --> 00:17:08,978
Religija. Zanimljivo.

178
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:12,716
Utjelovljenje Boga Rame

179
00:17:12,717 --> 00:17:16,369
u svojoj desnoj ruci dri to?

180
00:18:01,736 --> 00:18:05,012
Bjei!

181
00:18:09,789 --> 00:18:11,557
Salim, Jamal! Bjeite!

182
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,086
Oni su Muslimani, sredite ih!

183
00:19:13,284 --> 00:19:15,711
Bjei! Bjei sa nama!

184
00:19:26,215 --> 00:19:27,850
Hej, gubi se!

185
00:19:27,851 --> 00:19:31,322
Jesi li gluh? Rekao sam gubi se!

186
00:19:36,035 --> 00:19:37,866
Doi sa nama.

187
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:54,540
Budim se svako jutro sa eljom da
nisam znao odgovor na to pitanje.

188
00:19:58,035 --> 00:20:02,000
Da nije bilo Rame i Alaha...

189
00:20:02,035 --> 00:20:05,524
jo uvijek bi imao majku.

190
00:20:14,865 --> 00:20:16,649
Luk i strijela.

191
00:20:17,103 --> 00:20:18,326
Konani odgovor?

192
00:20:20,863 --> 00:20:22,055
Konani odgovor.

193
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:27,168
Kompjuter, D?

194
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,250
Osvojio si 16,000 rupija.

195
00:20:37,138 --> 00:20:39,357
Jako dobro, prijatelju.

196
00:20:41,647 --> 00:20:44,123
Vrijeme za reklame.
Nemojte otii.

197
00:20:46,035 --> 00:20:47,965
Imao si sree, ha?

198
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,261
Da sam na tvom mjestu, uzeo bih
novac i otiao.

199
00:20:51,035 --> 00:20:53,065
Nee ii dalje.

200
00:21:27,035 --> 00:21:28,499
Bjei!

201
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:30,690
Dovest e ovdje osiguranje!

202
00:21:30,691 --> 00:21:32,099
Pusti ju unutra.

203
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:36,462
Ona moe biti trei muketir.

204
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:41,891
Ja sam sad najstariji, i ja
kaem da ona ne ulazi, u redu?

205
00:21:43,035 --> 00:21:43,999
U svakom sluaju...

206
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:48,039
ak niti ne znamo ime treeg
prokletog muketira.

207
00:22:08,192 --> 00:22:09,538
Salim?

208
00:22:26,035 --> 00:22:27,707
Doi ovdje.

209
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,911
Gdje ti je majka?

210
00:22:45,035 --> 00:22:46,930
Otac?

211
00:22:50,656 --> 00:22:52,150
Ja sam Jamal.

212
00:22:52,185 --> 00:22:54,480
Ovo je moj brat, Salim.

213
00:22:56,035 --> 00:22:57,892
Ja sam Latika.

214
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,909
Moe spavati ovdje ako eli.

215
00:23:08,035 --> 00:23:09,987
Hvala ti, Jamal.

216
00:23:25,950 --> 00:23:28,144
Dobrodoli natrag u "Milijunaa".

217
00:23:28,179 --> 00:23:32,000
Na natjecatelj, Jamal Malik,
pomonik u pozivnom centru iz Mumbaya,

218
00:23:32,035 --> 00:23:33,577
je na 16 tisua rupija,

219
00:23:34,006 --> 00:23:37,322
i do sada je iskoristio samo
jednu pomo, pitaj publiku.

220
00:23:39,035 --> 00:23:42,638
Onda, moj prijatelju, ide na
ozbiljne novce.

221
00:23:44,035 --> 00:23:45,794
Hoemo li igrati dalje?

222
00:23:46,035 --> 00:23:47,515
Da.

223
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:58,000
Pjesmu "Darshan Do Ghanshyam" je
napisao koji poznati Indijski pisac?

224
00:23:58,035 --> 00:24:00,517
A: Surdas

225
00:24:00,552 --> 00:24:02,776
B: Tulsidas

226
00:24:02,811 --> 00:24:04,608
C: Mira Bai

227
00:24:05,038 --> 00:24:07,312
D: Kabir

228
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:10,948
Vrue je, ha?

229
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:05,252
Nain kako se odnosi prema nama,
sigurno je dobar ovjek.

230
00:26:05,253 --> 00:26:06,999
Sigurno je prokleti svetac.

231
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,275
Ne smijemo priati meu sobom.

232
00:26:09,276 --> 00:26:10,999
Zato?

233
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:15,417
Ako dobijemo repete, onda
je sigurno svetac.

234
00:26:35,035 --> 00:26:37,902
Jako dobro, Arvind. Jako dobro.

235
00:26:51,038 --> 00:26:53,634
Smije mi se. Ubit u te.

236
00:26:53,635 --> 00:26:56,051
Hej, pusti ju.

237
00:26:56,452 --> 00:26:58,460
Ne diraj me!

238
00:26:58,461 --> 00:27:00,030
Ti debeli prokletnie!

239
00:27:02,326 --> 00:27:03,967
Ti veliko drvo!

240
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:06,430
Punnoose, mislim da smo si
nali psa.

241
00:27:20,035 --> 00:27:23,556
U redu, idemo. Vrijeme je za posao.

242
00:27:31,759 --> 00:27:33,607
Mislite da ste doli ovdje
na piknik?

243
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:37,868
to mislite da su ovo, praznici?

244
00:27:40,035 --> 00:27:42,791
A zato se ti smije?

245
00:27:46,635 --> 00:27:48,165
Daj mi to.

246
00:27:53,091 --> 00:27:53,803
uti!

247
00:27:54,529 --> 00:27:55,263
Brat Salim.

248
00:27:55,791 --> 00:27:57,676
to je, mali brate, ima problema?

249
00:27:57,677 --> 00:27:59,675
Hej, uzmi ju. Ona je tvoja danas.

250
00:27:59,676 --> 00:28:01,063
Ne elim ju.

251
00:28:01,064 --> 00:28:04,207
Uzmi ju. To je za tvoje dobro.
Bebe zarauju duplo.

252
00:28:04,208 --> 00:28:06,535
Rekla je da ju ne eli.

253
00:28:06,536 --> 00:28:07,512
uti, Jamal!

254
00:28:08,849 --> 00:28:11,339
Uzmi ju odmah ili u
ju ispustiti.

255
00:28:15,935 --> 00:28:19,310
Neka nastavi plakati, i zaradit
e trostruko.

256
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:23,638
Hajde! Na posao!

257
00:28:49,035 --> 00:28:52,783
Uzet emo one najljue.

258
00:29:46,645 --> 00:29:51,657
Chilli na pimpeku!

259
00:29:57,932 --> 00:29:59,532
Vratit u vam to!

260
00:30:01,276 --> 00:30:03,150
Vraajte se svi na spavanje!

261
00:30:28,035 --> 00:30:31,419
Jako dobro. Sretan sam.

262
00:30:32,217 --> 00:30:35,541
Spreman je. -I ja sam spreman.

263
00:30:51,035 --> 00:30:52,846
Hajde, priblii lampu.

264
00:31:37,035 --> 00:31:38,815
U redu.

265
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,714
Dovedi Jamala.

266
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:07,517
Sluaj, mali. Sad je vrijeme
da odlui.

267
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:12,193
eli li ivot skitnice ili
ivot pravog ovjeka, ha?

268
00:32:12,228 --> 00:32:15,999
Pravog ovjeka. Revolveraa.

269
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:19,164
Sudbina ti je u rukama, ovjee.

270
00:32:20,035 --> 00:32:23,939
Moe biti kao ja ili...

271
00:32:26,035 --> 00:32:27,390
Jesi li razumio?

272
00:32:31,394 --> 00:32:32,611
Razumio sam.

273
00:32:34,574 --> 00:32:36,934
Idi. Dovedi Jamala.

274
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:50,249
Samo mi treba da se Mamanu svidi
moje pjevanje, i imat emo novaca.

275
00:32:50,250 --> 00:32:52,999
Puno novaca, Latika.

276
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:55,497
I onda to? Moemo i prestati
prositi?

277
00:32:55,498 --> 00:32:57,913
Prositi? ali se?

278
00:32:57,914 --> 00:33:00,337
ivjet emo u kui u
Harbour Roadu.

279
00:33:00,338 --> 00:33:03,385
Ti, ja i Salim. Tri muketira.

280
00:33:03,386 --> 00:33:05,230
Harbour Road. Stvarno?

281
00:33:05,231 --> 00:33:06,524
Da.

282
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,000
Na mjeseini...

283
00:33:11,035 --> 00:33:11,965
Ti i ja.

284
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:14,972
Plesat e sa mnom, hoe li?

285
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:20,683
Nadam se da bolje pjeva
nego to plee.

286
00:33:26,035 --> 00:33:29,706
Moj je red. -Pjevaj dobro.

287
00:33:36,850 --> 00:33:39,257
Znai to je to, ha, brate?

288
00:33:41,986 --> 00:33:44,389
Bolji ivote, dolazimo.

289
00:33:46,035 --> 00:33:47,943
Athos.

290
00:33:49,390 --> 00:33:50,960
Porthos?

291
00:33:52,872 --> 00:33:54,714
Kad kaem.

292
00:34:11,404 --> 00:34:13,000
Vrijeme je za postati profesionalac.

293
00:34:13,035 --> 00:34:14,965
to? Stvarno?

294
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:17,860
Prvo daj da ujem pjesmu...

295
00:34:19,035 --> 00:34:21,888
Darshan to Ghanshyam.

296
00:34:22,667 --> 00:34:24,323
To mi je omiljena.

297
00:34:29,035 --> 00:34:32,335
Pedeset rupija.

298
00:34:35,753 --> 00:34:37,730
Sad sam profesionalac,
to mogu?

299
00:34:38,322 --> 00:34:39,513
Prepredenjak.

300
00:34:42,164 --> 00:34:43,974
Evo ga.

301
00:35:04,861 --> 00:35:07,559
Jamal, bjei!

302
00:35:07,594 --> 00:35:09,689
Uhvatite ih!

303
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:15,833
Uzmite baklje! Uhvatite ih!

304
00:35:40,035 --> 00:35:42,071
Latika, bjei!

305
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:16,811
Hajde, Latika! Uhvati mi ruku!

306
00:36:34,252 --> 00:36:36,314
to se dogodilo, to se dogodilo?

307
00:36:36,349 --> 00:36:38,829
Pustila je!

308
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:49,034
Moramo se vratiti, brate.
Moramo se vratiti.

309
00:36:49,035 --> 00:36:51,034
Ako se vratimo, mrtvi smo.

310
00:36:51,035 --> 00:36:52,999
Jesi li poludio?

311
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:56,789
Htio ti je izvaditi oi!

312
00:36:56,790 --> 00:36:58,571
Sa licom.

313
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:11,384
Ne brini se za nju.
Bit e ona dobro.

314
00:37:12,035 --> 00:37:15,861
Uvijek je bila dobro.

315
00:37:31,035 --> 00:37:34,583
Surdas.

316
00:37:40,776 --> 00:37:43,426
Surdas?

317
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:50,915
Surdas, konani odgovor?

318
00:37:51,035 --> 00:37:53,189
Da.

319
00:37:57,000 --> 00:38:02,277
Zna to, u pravu si!

320
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:12,240
Slijepi pjevai zarade duplo,
zna li to?

321
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:16,356
to se dogodilo sa curom?
I nju su oslijepili?

322
00:38:19,035 --> 00:38:21,812
Imali su druge planove.

323
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:26,345
Trebalo mi je dugo vremena
da saznam koje.

324
00:38:46,035 --> 00:38:47,965
Mora to pustiti.

325
00:38:50,035 --> 00:38:52,035
Idemo.

326
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:55,894
Kuda? -Jako sam gladan.

327
00:40:12,535 --> 00:40:14,035
Dii se!

328
00:40:15,535 --> 00:40:18,535
Je li ti to tatin vlak?

329
00:41:40,035 --> 00:41:43,768
Je li ovo raj?

330
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:49,255
Nisi mrtav, Jamal.

331
00:41:50,035 --> 00:41:52,051
to je ovo?

332
00:41:52,052 --> 00:41:54,236
Neki hotel, ha?

333
00:41:55,000 --> 00:42:00,938
Taj Mahal je najljepi
primjer moderne arhitekture.

334
00:42:04,750 --> 00:42:09,734
...zavren je negdje oko 1648.
uz pomo oko 20,000 radnika.

335
00:42:10,068 --> 00:42:15,644
1980 je postao zatien od
strane UNESCO-a...

336
00:42:27,035 --> 00:42:30,070
Slubeni vodi.

337
00:42:30,105 --> 00:42:32,272
Molim Vas skinite cipele

338
00:42:50,035 --> 00:42:52,775
molim, molim.

339
00:42:52,776 --> 00:42:54,299
Kada je slijedea tura?

340
00:42:54,300 --> 00:42:56,825
Nemamo ba puno vremena.

341
00:42:56,826 --> 00:42:58,437
Moramo jo pogledati Red
Fort ovo poslijepodne.

342
00:42:58,438 --> 00:42:59,999
POSJETIOCI MORAJU UZETI
POTVRDU

343
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:03,899
Ne, ja... -Da li biste nas mogli
odmah provesti okolo?

344
00:43:03,900 --> 00:43:09,882
Razumijemo da e kotati malo
vie za samo nas dvoje.

345
00:43:09,883 --> 00:43:12,459
Ali naravno, gospoo!

346
00:43:13,089 --> 00:43:14,473
Molim Vas pratite me.

347
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:18,965
Taj Mahal je sagradio car
Khurrama

348
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:24,500
za svoju enu Mumtaz, koja je
bila najljepa ena na svijet.

349
00:43:24,535 --> 00:43:30,000
kada je ona umrla, car je
odluio napraviti ovaj divan hotel,

350
00:43:30,035 --> 00:43:32,965
za svakoga tko se odlui posjetiti
njenu grobnicu.

351
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:39,000
Ali on je umro 1587. prije nego
to su napravljene sobe i liftovi.

352
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:46,000
Ali ovaj bazen koji vidite je bio
gotov na vrijeme, i jako moderan.

353
00:43:47,035 --> 00:43:49,965
U vodiu ne pie nita o tome.

354
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:56,000
Vodi su napisali bezvezni
Indijski prosjaci.

355
00:43:58,035 --> 00:44:03,000
A ovo, dame i gospodo, je
poivalite od Mumtaz.

356
00:44:03,035 --> 00:44:05,965
Kako je umrla?

357
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:08,500
Prometna nesrea. -Stvarno?

358
00:44:08,535 --> 00:44:10,965
Puno rtava.

359
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:14,965
Mislio sam da je umrla na porodu.

360
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:20,000
Tono, gospodine. Bila je na
putu u bolnicu kad se to dogodilo.

361
00:44:26,035 --> 00:44:28,847
Spremni?

362
00:44:29,934 --> 00:44:31,343
osmjeh.

363
00:44:38,477 --> 00:44:41,568
Cipele! Amerike cipele!

364
00:45:03,035 --> 00:45:06,593
Osmjeh.

365
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:24,000
Ovo, g. David, je najvei
Dhobi Ghat u cijeloj Indiji.

366
00:45:24,035 --> 00:45:25,965
To je udesno.

367
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:29,000
Doite, pogledajte ovo.

368
00:45:29,035 --> 00:45:31,965
Kau da svaki ovjek u
Uttar Pradeshu

369
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:38,000
nosi kurtu koja je barem
jednom bila oprana ovdje.

370
00:45:44,371 --> 00:45:49,242
Bre malo! Brzina kao u pit-stopu
na utrkama! Kao kod Schumachera!

371
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:54,508
Jesu li to krave ili buffala...
to je ono tamo?

372
00:46:03,035 --> 00:46:04,965
Oh, sranje.

373
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:05,965
to se to dovraga dogodilo
ovdje?

374
00:46:15,035 --> 00:46:16,965
Stani malo!

375
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
Imate osiguranje, zar ne?

376
00:46:19,395 --> 00:46:20,155
Jesi li dobro?

377
00:46:20,618 --> 00:46:23,196
Htjeli ste vidjeti pravu
Indiju? Ovo je to!

378
00:46:25,500 --> 00:46:27,975
Evo malo i prave Amerike, sine.

379
00:46:28,548 --> 00:46:30,000
("Novac")

380
00:46:30,309 --> 00:46:31,635
Oh, da, da! Isuse...

381
00:46:35,011 --> 00:46:35,932
Evo.

382
00:48:19,848 --> 00:48:23,000
Na novanici od 100 dolara

383
00:48:23,001 --> 00:48:27,125
je portret kojeg Amerikog
dravnika?

384
00:48:28,035 --> 00:48:31,051
A: George Washingtona

385
00:48:31,052 --> 00:48:34,560
B: Franklin Roosevelta

386
00:48:34,561 --> 00:48:38,083
C: Benjamin Franklina

387
00:48:38,084 --> 00:48:41,480
D: Abraham Lincolna

388
00:48:44,942 --> 00:48:49,465
Isplata ili igra dalje, Jamal?

389
00:48:50,035 --> 00:48:52,835
Odlui.

390
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:57,000
Boe, on gleda u kameru,
nema pojma koji je odgovor.

391
00:48:57,035 --> 00:49:00,017
Sad e otii. Budite spremni.

392
00:49:00,052 --> 00:49:03,000
Ne, prvo e se malo
poigrati s njim.

393
00:49:03,035 --> 00:49:04,965
Jamal?

394
00:49:05,000 --> 00:49:10,150
Jesi li u svom poslu imao puno
doticaja s novanicama od 100 dolara?

395
00:49:10,185 --> 00:49:13,965
Minimalna napojnica za
moje uslugu.

396
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:17,000
Sad znam zato su mi
rauni za mobitel tako visoki.

397
00:49:17,035 --> 00:49:21,000
Daju napojnice posluitelju
od 100 dolara.

398
00:49:21,035 --> 00:49:23,517
Odgovor je C. Benjamin Franklin.

399
00:49:23,552 --> 00:49:25,965
Igra dalje, ha?

400
00:49:26,000 --> 00:49:28,000
Mislim da upravo jesam, zar ne?

401
00:49:28,035 --> 00:49:30,017
Igrao si C, zar ne?

402
00:49:30,052 --> 00:49:32,000
Tko je na novanici
od 1,000 rupija?

403
00:49:32,035 --> 00:49:34,495
Ne znam.

404
00:49:35,052 --> 00:49:36,604
Ne zna?

405
00:49:38,315 --> 00:49:39,725
Ghandi je.

406
00:49:40,692 --> 00:49:42,821
Oh, uo sam za njega.

407
00:49:46,035 --> 00:49:46,965
Nemoj mi se praviti pametan

408
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:50,000
jer u ponovno donijeti struju.

409
00:49:50,035 --> 00:49:51,965
Pogledaj.

410
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:56,000
Nisu me pitali to pitanje.
ne znam zato.

411
00:49:56,035 --> 00:49:57,965
Pitajte ih.

412
00:49:58,000 --> 00:50:04,000
Smijeno je, izgleda da te
ba ne zanima jako novac.

413
00:50:04,035 --> 00:50:07,107
injenica je da ima...

414
00:50:07,337 --> 00:50:11,518
jedan milijun rupija!

415
00:50:14,947 --> 00:50:18,203
Objasni novanicu od 100 dolara.

416
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:23,346
Bombay je promijenio ime
u Mumbay.

417
00:50:26,035 --> 00:50:27,854
Zato ne razumije?

418
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:02,965
Djevojka je ivjela ovdje.
Visoka je otprilike kao ja.

419
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:07,019
Zvala se Latika.
Ne znam nikoga po tom imenu.

420
00:51:35,464 --> 00:51:39,590
Dva pilea burgera, dva pomfrija,
jedna dijetna kola, jedna coca cola!

421
00:51:39,591 --> 00:51:41,351
Jedna mineralna!

422
00:51:44,035 --> 00:51:45,978
Shimla.

423
00:51:47,000 --> 00:51:51,500
Idem u Chowpatty, ok?
Ide sa mnom?

424
00:51:51,535 --> 00:51:56,000
Za ime Boga, jesi li zdrav?

425
00:51:56,035 --> 00:51:58,517
Silom eli natrag u tu rupu.

426
00:51:58,552 --> 00:52:01,000
Ostavili smo nae prijatelje,
dobar ivot,

427
00:52:01,035 --> 00:52:03,017
puno novca. Zbog ovoga?!

428
00:52:03,052 --> 00:52:04,965
Vratili smo se da ju naemo.

429
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:08,500
Ti si to napravio. Mene nije
briga za nju.

430
00:52:08,535 --> 00:52:12,000
Ima dosta pica u Bombayu
za Salima.

431
00:52:12,035 --> 00:52:12,965
Oh da!

432
00:52:13,000 --> 00:52:16,000
Trebao bi doi u Kaveze
u subotu naveer,

433
00:52:16,035 --> 00:52:20,000
umjesto da traga za
svojom izgubljenom ljubavi.

434
00:52:20,035 --> 00:52:22,517
Idem u Chowpatty.

435
00:52:22,552 --> 00:52:24,965
Idem u Chowpatty!

436
00:52:25,000 --> 00:52:29,000
Ima 19 milijuna ljudi u
ovom gradu, Jamal.

437
00:52:29,035 --> 00:52:32,000
Zaboravi na nju.

438
00:52:32,035 --> 00:52:35,489
Ona je "stree"(mlada Indijska
plesaica).

439
00:52:54,541 --> 00:52:56,040
Pozdrav, gospodine.

440
00:52:56,041 --> 00:52:59,988
Blagoslovljeni bili oni
koji ine dobro drugima.

441
00:53:09,035 --> 00:53:11,517
Dolari. Koliko?

442
00:53:11,518 --> 00:53:14,534
100. -Misli da sam budala.

443
00:53:14,535 --> 00:53:17,940
asna rije. Kunem se
duom moje majke.

444
00:53:17,941 --> 00:53:24,440
to je na ovoj novanici?
ija je slika gore?

445
00:53:24,441 --> 00:53:26,965
Stari ovjek...

446
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:31,000
elav je na vrhu glave, sa dugom
kosom sa strane, kao curica.

447
00:53:31,035 --> 00:53:33,229
Benjamin Franklin.

448
00:53:38,000 --> 00:53:43,034
Sad si veliki deko, Jamal.

449
00:53:43,035 --> 00:53:45,517
Drago mi je zbog tebe.

450
00:53:45,552 --> 00:53:47,965
Oprosti...

451
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:51,000
Spasio si mog prijatelja.
Ja nisam bio te sree.

452
00:53:51,035 --> 00:53:53,517
To je jedina razlika.

453
00:53:53,552 --> 00:53:55,776
Arvind, pokuavam nai...

454
00:53:55,811 --> 00:53:58,000
Duan si Mamanu. Dri se dalje
od njega.

455
00:53:58,035 --> 00:54:00,460
On nikada ne zaboravlja.

456
00:54:00,461 --> 00:54:02,983
Dugujem Latiki.

457
00:54:05,000 --> 00:54:05,965
iva je, zar ne?

458
00:54:06,000 --> 00:54:11,809
Vie nego iva. Ona je u ulici
Pila. Zovu je Cherry.

459
00:54:14,035 --> 00:54:15,880
Hvala.

460
00:54:21,100 --> 00:54:23,198
Pjevat u ti na sprovodu.

461
00:55:45,000 --> 00:55:48,786
Onda, je li to ona ili ne?

462
00:55:55,035 --> 00:55:57,550
Ona je seksi, ovjee!

463
00:56:04,000 --> 00:56:04,965
Tko je to? -Jamal?

464
00:56:05,000 --> 00:56:08,000
Uzet u torbe.
-Tko si ti? to eli?

465
00:56:08,035 --> 00:56:11,000
Glupi deki! -Pokupi to.

466
00:56:11,035 --> 00:56:13,035
Kako si me naao?

467
00:56:18,000 --> 00:56:19,265
Uzmi novac. Hajde!

468
00:56:19,266 --> 00:56:21,017
Imamo sve. Idemo!

469
00:56:22,000 --> 00:56:23,789
Sranje.

470
00:56:25,000 --> 00:56:28,031
Gle tko je to ovdje!

471
00:56:29,639 --> 00:56:31,245
Pozdrav ponovo.

472
00:56:31,687 --> 00:56:36,281
Jamal, Salim.

473
00:56:37,310 --> 00:56:39,048
Nikad ne zaboravljam lice.

474
00:56:40,035 --> 00:56:40,965
Imam nos za to,

475
00:56:41,000 --> 00:56:44,319
posebno za one koje posjedujem.

476
00:56:47,000 --> 00:56:53,000
Stvarno ste mislili da ete samo
doi i uzeti moje blago?

477
00:56:53,035 --> 00:56:55,730
Latika, doi.

478
00:57:00,000 --> 00:57:05,771
Imate li pojma koliko ova mala
nevina curica vrijedi?

479
00:57:06,172 --> 00:57:09,109
Molim nastavite, gospodine Ji.
-U redu, gospodine.

480
00:57:09,110 --> 00:57:11,468
Vadite ih van! -Ne!

481
00:57:18,320 --> 00:57:20,939
Hajde! Tamo!

482
00:57:22,000 --> 00:57:26,500
