Izgovara se: "Kee-nu-ssi".

607
01:09:09,035 --> 01:09:11,965
Odakle si ti? Negdje blizu?

608
01:09:12,000 --> 01:09:16,000
Malo nie niz vau
ulicu, gospoo MacKintosh.

609
01:09:16,035 --> 01:09:17,970
Blizu "locha".

610
01:09:17,971 --> 01:09:20,699
