Misli da e mi rei?

724
01:22:37,024 --> 01:22:38,946
Ne! Ne! Ne!

725
01:22:59,000 --> 01:23:02,482
Kakvo je ovo sranje?

726
01:23:02,483 --> 01:23:06,323
Izlazi! Izlazi!

727
01:23:12,000 --> 01:23:16,965
Hajde, prije nego nas oboje ubije.

728
01:23:17,000 --> 01:23:20,000
Moe li neto napraviti
za mene? -Sve.

729
01:23:20,035 --> 01:23:22,000
Onda me zaboravi.

730
01:23:22,035 --> 01:23:23,965
to? Ne.

731
01:23:24,000 --> 01:23:31,000
ekat u. VT stanica.
5 sati, svaki dan dok ne doe.

732
01:23:34,035 --> 01:23:36,965
Volim te.

733
01:23:37,000 --> 01:23:44,000
Pa to onda?
Prekasno je, Jamal. Idi sada.

734
01:23:52,035 --> 01:23:52,965
Pa, Jamal.

735
01:23:53,000 --> 01:23:58,000
Koji igra kriketa je napravio
najvie bodova u povijesti?

736
01:23:58,035 --> 01:24:00,017
A:Sachin Tendulkar

737
01:24:00,052 --> 01:24:02,526
B:Ricky Ponting

738
01:24:02,561 --> 01:24:06,280
C:Michael Slater

739
01:24:06,315 --> 01:24:09,965
D:Jack Hobbs

740
01:24:10,000 --> 01:24:15,000
Ali, zapamti, ako krivo odgovori,

741
01:24:15,035 --> 01:24:20,000
samo tako e izgubiti sve.

742
01:24:20,035 --> 01:24:27,035
Pa, da li eli ovo odgovoriti?

743
01:24:47,223 --> 01:24:51,800
Toliko snova...

744
01:24:51,801 --> 01:24:53,474
na podu.

745
01:27:36,000 --> 01:27:40,000
Vrijeme za reklame,
dame i gospodo.

746
01:27:40,035 --> 01:27:44,000
Znam, znam. Ni ja ne mogu
podnijeti pritisak.

747
01:27:44,035 --> 01:27:48,035
Vratit emo se odmah.

748
01:27:56,000 --> 01:28:01,000
Deko iz sirotinjskog kraja
postaje milijuna preko noi.

749
01:28:01,035 --> 01:28:06,000
Zna kome je to jo
jedino uspjelo?

750
01:28:06,035 --> 01:28:07,965
Meni.

751
01:28:10,000 --> 01:28:11,965
Znam kakav je to osjeaj.

752
01:28:12,000 --> 01:28:14,965
Znam kroz to prolazi.

753
01:28:15,000 --> 01:28:18,000
Ja neu postati milijuna.

754
01:28:18,035 --> 01:28:21,017
Ne znam odgovor.

755
01:28:21,052 --> 01:28:23,526
Rekao si to i prije, da...

756
01:28:23,561 --> 01:28:25,965
Stvarno, ovaj put ne znam.

757
01:28:26,000 --> 01:28:32,000
Hajde, ne moe sada
uzeti lovu i pobjei.

758
01:28:32,035 --> 01:28:35,017
Ti si na pragu da ue u povijest.

759
01:28:35,052 --> 01:28:38,526
Ne znam to jo mogu napraviti.

760
01:28:38,561 --> 01:28:41,965
Moda je to napisano, prijatelju.

761
01:28:42,000 --> 01:28:47,000
Imam neki osjeaj
da e ovo osvojiti.

762
01:28:47,035 --> 01:28:54,035
Vjeruj mi, Jamal.

763
01:29:05,552 --> 01:29:12,552
Osvojit e ovo.

764
01:29:24,000 --> 01:29:26,878
Pripremite se svi.
U eteru smo za 13...

765
01:29:30,887 --> 01:29:32,516
Da, otiao je. Samo dajem...

766
01:29:34,813 --> 01:29:36,149
Hajde, bre.

767
01:29:37,000 --> 01:29:38,970
20 sekundi!

768
01:29:44,000 --> 01:29:46,000
Napravi pravu stvar i za,
oko 3 minute,

769
01:29:46,035 --> 01:29:49,395
bit e popularan kao i ja.

770
01:29:49,396 --> 01:29:50,965
10 sekundi!

771
01:29:51,000 --> 01:29:56,000
I bogat kao i ja. Skoro kao ja.

772
01:29:56,035 --> 01:29:58,965
5 sekundi! 4... 3...

773
01:29:59,000 --> 01:30:03,332
Od siromaha do bogataa.
To je tvoja sudbina.

774
01:30:03,333 --> 01:30:08,837
U eteru smo.
Pljesak i glazbu, molim!

775
01:30:19,466 --> 01:30:22,965
Dobro doli natrag u
"Tko eli biti milijuna?"!

776
01:30:23,000 --> 01:30:29,000
U stolici je veeras Jamal
Malik, kao da to ne znamo.

777
01:30:29,035 --> 01:30:32,517
Za 10 milijuna rupija.

778
01:30:32,552 --> 01:30:35,965
Treba ponovno odgovoriti.

779
01:30:36,000 --> 01:30:43,000
Koji igra kriketa je napravio
najvie bodova u povijesti?

780
01:30:44,035 --> 01:30:46,000
Ne, to nije Sachin Tendulkar.

781
01:30:46,035 --> 01:30:47,965
To je poetak.

782
01:30:48,000 --> 01:30:55,000
Pa, mogao bi biti Ricky Ponting,
Jack Hobbs ili Michael Slater.

783
01:30:55,035 --> 01:30:58,000
Koristit u pomo. Pola-pola.

784
01:30:58,035 --> 01:30:59,965
Ok.

785
01:31:00,000 --> 01:31:06,000
Molim vas da maknete
dva pogrena odgovora.

786
01:31:06,035 --> 01:31:09,017
Pa, bio si u pravu
za Sachin Tendulkara.

787
01:31:09,052 --> 01:31:12,000
To ti ostavlja jo dvije
mogunosti, Jamal.

788
01:31:12,035 --> 01:31:16,000
B: Ricky Ponting
ili D: Jack Hobbs.

789
01:31:16,035 --> 01:31:19,965
to misli?

790
01:31:20,000 --> 01:31:26,000
Vrijeme odluke.
Za 10 milijuna rupija.

791
01:31:26,035 --> 01:31:30,000
B: Ricky Ponting

792
01:31:30,001 --> 01:31:33,052
ili D: Jack Hobbs.

793
01:31:46,035 --> 01:31:51,517
D.

794
01:31:51,552 --> 01:31:56,965
Ne B?

795
01:31:57,000 --> 01:32:03,000
Ricky Ponting,
veliki Australski igra kriketa?

796
01:32:03,035 --> 01:32:07,000
D, Jack Hobbs.

797
01:32:07,035 --> 01:32:11,965
Zna?

798
01:32:12,000 --> 01:32:15,000
Pa, mogao bi biti B,
Ricky Ponting?

799
01:32:15,035 --> 01:32:19,517
Ili D, Jack Hobbs.

800
01:32:19,552 --> 01:32:23,965
Konani odgovor, D.

801
01:32:24,000 --> 01:32:28,000
Raunalo, D.

802
01:32:28,035 --> 01:32:35,035
D.

803
01:32:44,000 --> 01:32:51,000
Sa 197 bodova, odgovor je...

804
01:32:52,035 --> 01:32:58,965
D, Jack Hobbs!

805
01:32:59,000 --> 01:33:06,000
Jamal Malik! Milijuna!

806
01:33:06,173 --> 01:33:13,173
Plei! Hajde!

807
01:33:15,246 --> 01:33:18,097
Bravo! Bravo.

808
01:33:42,000 --> 01:33:46,000
Da li si spreman za zadnje pitanje?

809
01:33:46,035 --> 01:33:52,965
Za 20 milijuna rupija.

810
01:33:53,000 --> 01:34:00,000
Ne. Ali moda je napisano.

811
01:34:00,035 --> 01:34:02,965
Moda.

812
01:34:03,000 --> 01:34:09,500
Ok. Zadnje pitanje!
Na "Tko eli biti...

813
01:34:09,535 --> 01:34:16,000
Koji show, dame i gospodo!
Koji show!

814
01:34:16,035 --> 01:34:16,965
Pridruite nam se sutra naveer

815
01:34:17,000 --> 01:34:24,000
da vidite da li e Jamal Malik
napraviti najveu greku svom ivotu.

816
01:34:25,035 --> 01:34:32,017
Ovuda.

817
01:34:32,052 --> 01:34:38,965
Super show.

818
01:34:39,000 --> 01:34:40,400
Vidimo se sutra, ok.

819
01:34:40,435 --> 01:34:43,035
Doi na vrijeme. Bok.

820
01:34:53,552 --> 01:35:00,552
to se dogaa?

821
01:35:01,000 --> 01:35:06,965
- On vara.
- Kako zna da vara?

822
01:35:07,000 --> 01:35:12,000
Dao sam mu pogrean
odgovor, a on je ispravno odgovorio.

823
01:35:12,035 --> 01:35:14,965
Dao si mu odgovor?

824
01:35:15,000 --> 01:35:21,000
Ne ba tako. Ali to sada nije
vano. To je moj show!

825
01:35:21,035 --> 01:35:28,035
Moj jebeni show!

826
01:35:34,000 --> 01:35:38,500
To je bizarno prihvatljivo,
ali ipak...

827
01:35:38,535 --> 01:35:43,000
Zato to sam iz sirotinjskog
kraja, posluitelj,

828
01:35:43,035 --> 01:35:44,517
zato sam laljivac?

829
01:35:44,552 --> 01:35:45,965
Veina vas je.

830
01:35:46,000 --> 01:35:51,000
Ali ti nisi laljivac, g. Malik.
To je sigurno.

831
01:35:51,035 --> 01:35:56,000
I previe si iskren.

832
01:35:56,035 --> 01:36:00,965
Gotovi smo.

833
01:36:01,000 --> 01:36:08,000
Ne znam kuda su je odveli.

834
01:36:10,035 --> 01:36:17,035
Latika.

835
01:36:20,000 --> 01:36:27,000
Otiao sam na show jer
sam mislio da e ona gledati.

836
01:36:38,000 --> 01:36:43,000
Jamal Malik, neobrazovani 18-godinjak
deko iz sirotinjskog kraja Mumbaya,

837
01:36:43,035 --> 01:36:46,965
jedan je korak od dobitka,

838
01:36:47,000 --> 01:36:49,965
i ljudi oko mene postavljaju
jo jedno vee pitanje:

839
01:36:50,000 --> 01:36:57,000
Da li e se vratiti veeras
na borbu za 20 milijuna rupija?

840
01:37:30,035 --> 01:37:36,000
Hej, daj mi pusu.

841
01:37:36,035 --> 01:37:42,965
Hajde, djevojko!

842
01:37:43,000 --> 01:37:47,000
Da, ne mogu nita uti od buke.

843
01:37:47,135 --> 01:37:49,065
Mora nas vratiti u grad.

844
01:37:56,000 --> 01:38:00,000
Kao da nije bilo dovoljno drame
na putu do zadnjeg pitanja...

845
01:38:00,035 --> 01:38:05,000
Jamal Malik je sino uhien
zbog sumnje na prijevaru.

846
01:38:05,035 --> 01:38:12,035
Taj deko. Pametan je.

847
01:38:14,035 --> 01:38:21,035
Ludi "chudge".

848
01:38:23,035 --> 01:38:25,517
Evo, hajde.

849
01:38:25,552 --> 01:38:27,965
Ali...

850
01:38:28,000 --> 01:38:35,000
Samo vozi.
Nee biti druge prilike.

851
01:38:37,035 --> 01:38:43,965
Ubit e te.

852
01:38:44,000 --> 01:38:51,000
Ja u se pobrinuti za njega.

853
01:38:51,035 --> 01:38:56,035
Salim, ne mogu.

854
01:38:57,252 --> 01:38:59,152
Mora.

855
01:39:05,811 --> 01:39:12,811
Mora ovo napraviti.

856
01:39:13,000 --> 01:39:20,000
Za sve to sam napravio...
molim te, oprosti mi.

857
01:39:28,035 --> 01:39:35,035
Imaj dobar ivot.

858
01:40:01,000 --> 01:40:08,000
Vraa se u show.

859
01:40:33,035 --> 01:40:40,035
Hajde!

860
01:40:52,000 --> 01:40:55,965
Jamal? Milijuna?

861
01:40:56,000 --> 01:41:03,000
Multi-milijuna?
Onaj sa svom onom gotovinom?

862
01:41:03,035 --> 01:41:09,000
Hajde, idi sa mojim
blagoslovom i osvoji sve.

863
01:41:09,035 --> 01:41:13,965
Volimo te, Jamal!

864
01:41:14,000 --> 01:41:16,965
Naciju je ulovila milijunaka
groznica.

865
01:41:17,000 --> 01:41:21,000
Jamal Malik, neobrazovani deko
iz sirotinjskog kraja Mumbaya,

866
01:41:21,035 --> 01:41:24,333
je osvojio 10 milijuna rupija

867
01:41:24,368 --> 01:41:26,843
na kvizu "Tko eli biti milijuna",

868
01:41:28,000 --> 01:41:31,000
i oko 90 milijuna ljudi nas
veeras gleda

869
01:41:31,001 --> 01:41:35,001
da bi vidjelo da li e uspjeti
osvojiti 20 milijuna rupija.

870
01:42:02,036 --> 01:42:04,000
Gdje su svi? Vratit se ovamo!

871
01:42:04,035 --> 01:42:10,000
Vratite se na posao!

872
01:42:10,035 --> 01:42:17,035
Posluitelju?

873
01:42:33,000 --> 01:42:38,000
Dobro doli natrag u
"Tko eli biti milijuna".

874
01:42:38,035 --> 01:42:39,965
Mogu sa sigurnou rei
da je veeras

875
01:42:40,000 --> 01:42:43,965
najvea veer u ivotima
nas dvojice.

876
01:42:44,000 --> 01:42:47,000
Jamal Malik, radnik iz Mumbaya,

877
01:42:47,035 --> 01:42:48,965
je ve osvojio 10 milijuna.

878
01:42:49,000 --> 01:42:50,965
Moe otii sa tom
svotom u depu,

879
01:42:51,000 --> 01:42:54,000
ili napraviti najvee kockanje
u povijesti televizije.

880
01:42:54,035 --> 01:42:55,965
Moe odgovarati na
finalno pitanje

881
01:42:56,000 --> 01:43:01,000
i pokuati osvojiti
20 milijuna rupija.

882
01:43:01,035 --> 01:43:06,000
Da li si spreman za to pitanje?

883
01:43:06,035 --> 01:43:08,077
Da. -Jamal!

884
01:43:21,940 --> 01:43:24,330
Da li puno ita, Jamal?

885
01:43:26,298 --> 01:43:28,268
Znam itati.

886
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,965
Sretnie.

887
01:43:32,000 --> 01:43:38,000
U knjizi Alexandra Dumasa,
"Tri muketira",

888
01:43:38,035 --> 01:43:44,000
dva muketira su se zvala
Athos i Porthos.

889
01:43:44,035 --> 01:43:48,000
Koje je bilo ime treeg muketira?

890
01:43:48,035 --> 01:43:50,965
A: Aramis

891
01:43:51,000 --> 01:43:55,000
B: Kardinal Richelieu

892
01:43:55,035 --> 01:44:00,017
C: D'Artagnan

893
01:44:00,052 --> 01:44:04,965
D: Planchet

894
01:44:05,000 --> 01:44:07,965
Ona bi mogla biti trei muketir.

895
01:44:08,000 --> 01:44:11,000
Finalno pitanje za 20 milijuna
rupija, i on se smije.

896
01:44:11,035 --> 01:44:14,517
Mislim da zna odgovor.

897
01:44:14,552 --> 01:44:18,000
Vjeruje li, ja ne vjerujem.

898
01:44:18,035 --> 01:44:20,965
Ne zna?

899
01:44:21,000 --> 01:44:26,000
Znai uzet e 10 milijuna i otii?

900
01:44:26,035 --> 01:44:31,965
Ne. Igrat u.

901
01:44:32,000 --> 01:44:33,965
Da te podsjetim, Jamal.

902
01:44:34,000 --> 01:44:37,000
Ako pogreno odgovori,

903
01:44:37,035 --> 01:44:39,965
sve e izgubiti.

904
01:44:40,000 --> 01:44:44,000
10 milijuna rupija, Jamal.

905
01:44:44,035 --> 01:44:47,965
To je sudbina.

906
01:44:48,000 --> 01:44:51,500
elio bih nazvati prijatelja.

907
01:44:51,535 --> 01:44:54,965
Idemo na vezu.

908
01:44:55,000 --> 01:45:02,000
Zadnja pomo. Evo ga.

909
01:45:06,035 --> 01:45:10,517
Zvoni!

910
01:45:10,552 --> 01:45:14,965
Tko je?

911
01:45:15,000 --> 01:45:20,965
To je broj moga brata, ali...

912
01:45:21,000 --> 01:45:27,000
Brata koji nije kraj telefona
na pitanju za 20 milijuna rupija?

913
01:45:27,035 --> 01:45:34,035
To je jedini broj koji znam.

914
01:45:56,852 --> 01:45:58,552
Sada si sam sa sobom, Jamal.

915
01:46:02,035 --> 01:46:07,965
Halo?

916
01:46:08,000 --> 01:46:10,965
Halo, Jamal?

917
01:46:11,000 --> 01:46:16,000
Mislim da to nije tvoj brat.

918
01:46:16,035 --> 01:46:17,965
To je...

919
01:46:18,000 --> 01:46:19,000
Moje ime je Latika.

920
01:46:19,035 --> 01:46:20,965
Ok, Latika.

921
01:46:21,000 --> 01:46:26,000
eli li jo jednom uti pitanje?
I da raistimo...

922
01:46:26,035 --> 01:46:32,000
20 milijuna rupija za ovaj
odgovor, imate 30 sekundi.

923
01:46:32,035 --> 01:46:39,000
Jamal, molim te
da proita pitanje Latiki.

924
01:46:39,035 --> 01:46:41,965
To si stvarno ti? -Da.

925
01:46:42,000 --> 01:46:45,965
Pitanje, Jamal. Pitanje!

926
01:46:46,000 --> 01:46:48,500
U knjizi Alexandra Dumasa,
"Tri muketira",

927
01:46:48,535 --> 01:46:51,000
dva muketira su se zvala
Athos i Porthos.

928
01:46:51,035 --> 01:46:52,965
Koje je bilo ime treeg muketira?

929
01:46:53,000 --> 01:47:00,000
Da li je to A: Aramis, B: Kardinal
Richelieu, C: D'Artagnan ili D: Planchet?

930
01:47:00,035 --> 01:47:02,017
15 sekundi!

931
01:47:02,052 --> 01:47:04,026
Gdje si?

932
01:47:04,061 --> 01:47:06,030
Na sigurnom sam.

933
01:47:06,065 --> 01:47:07,965
10 sekundi!

934
01:47:08,000 --> 01:47:13,965
Latika, o emu razmilja?

935
01:47:14,000 --> 01:47:20,000
Ne znam. Nikada ne znam.

936
01:47:20,035 --> 01:47:27,035
Jamal, bez novca...

937
01:47:31,000 --> 01:47:36,000
Sada si preputen
sam sebi, Jamal.

938
01:47:36,235 --> 01:47:40,535
Tvoj zadnji odgovor
za 20 milijuna rupija.

939
01:47:52,035 --> 01:47:55,965
A.

940
01:47:56,000 --> 01:47:58,965
A, zato jer...?

941
01:47:59,000 --> 01:48:02,010
Samo... zato.

942
01:48:02,723 --> 01:48:04,066
Hej, Salim!

943
01:48:08,000 --> 01:48:10,965
Zadnji odgovor?

944
01:48:11,000 --> 01:48:17,000
Da, zadnji odgovor. A, Aramis.

945
01:48:17,535 --> 01:48:20,535
Kompjuter, A.

946
01:48:28,000 --> 01:48:33,000
Jamal Malik, radnik iz Mumbaya,

947
01:48:33,035 --> 01:48:35,965
posluitelj,

948
01:48:36,000 --> 01:48:38,965
u pitanju za 20 milijuna rupija

949
01:48:39,000 --> 01:48:46,000
bio si pitan kako se zvao trei
muketir u noveli Alexandera Dumasa.

950
01:48:46,035 --> 01:48:52,965
Ti si odgovorio A, Aramis.

951
01:48:53,000 --> 01:48:56,000
to je, moram ti rei...

952
01:48:56,035 --> 01:49:03,035
Ispravan odgovor!

953
01:49:23,035 --> 01:49:30,017
Jamal Malik!

954
01:49:30,052 --> 01:49:34,052
Bog je super.

955
01:49:37,261 --> 01:49:39,061
Koja veer!

956
01:52:13,000 --> 01:52:15,965
Znao sam da e gledati.

957
01:52:16,000 --> 01:52:23,000
Mislila sam da emo biti
zajedno samo u smrti.

958
01:53:04,035 --> 01:53:09,000
To je naa sudbina.

959
01:53:09,035 --> 01:53:16,035
Poljubi me.

960
01:53:19,000 --> 01:53:26,000
D: zapisano je

961
01:53:28,035 --> 01:53:30,000
